	- [gemini] starting download thread in ':rendering' status.

2020-08-29  cage

        * configure, src/gemini-viewer-metadata.lisp,
        src/gemini-viewer.lisp, src/open-message-link-window.lisp,
        src/program-events.lisp, tinmop.asd:

