	* src/package.lisp
	* src/tui-utils.lisp
	* src/ui-goodies.lisp
	* tinmop.asd

	- [gemini]
	  - using quri instead of puri library because the first has a better handling
            of UTF-8;
	- using binary stream instead of ASCII.

2020-07-02
	* src/gemini/gemini-parser.lisp
